title: This is not what MAGA campaigned on.

author: Russell Brand
description:
The G7 Summit just wrapped—and it was a circus of weakness, symbolism, and globalist posturing. From Starmer picking up Trump’s dropped trade deal to Macron getting everything wrong, I unpack what really went down. Trump may have shown strength at the table, but cracks in his base are starting to show. With growing splits over immigration and foreign wars, is this the moment Trump begins to lose the MAGA faithful? Let me know what you think in the comments and the chat.
